{"tid":589094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子食牛扒鯁親 女友臨急用刀片救佢一命","createTime":"2018-03-11T16:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T14:06:17.000Z","uid":3189,"like":1024,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"757bbc49f2614eacf06a52a62a89ba61287b95ef","tid":589094,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"一次牛扒鯁喉以後，他的女友多了一重身份－－他的救命恩人。新西蘭50歲男子貝斯特（Isak Bester）上周在家中燒烤期間，遭一塊牛扒鯁喉幾乎窒息，命懸一線之際，其任助產士的女友當機立斷，即場為他「開刀」開通氣道，挽回他一命。<br />\n<br />\n45歲的英雄女友格拉斯（Sarah Glass）是一名助產士，在20多年前受訓時學過氣管切開手術（tracheotomy），沒料如今大派用場救回另一半的性命。當天貝斯特遭一塊牛扒鯁喉，臉色發紫，她立即口對口為他做心肺復甦但無效，她憶述：「過了8分鐘左右，我們已不能送氣給他，那塊牛扒移動了，那時他的臉色已開始嚴重發紫，正在我們面前慢慢死去。」<br />\n<br />\n當時格拉斯大叫朋友拿來尖銳物，說要給男友的氣管開刀，結果有人遞上一塊刀片，她想也沒多想就在男友喉結下開刀，為氣管開洞，之後又在她的家庭分娩工具箱找來注射器和氧氧，確保可以為男友輸氣，貝斯特慢慢也回復氣息。約20分鐘後救援人員才抵達。<br />\n<br />\n「他倒在一片血泊中，我也滿手鮮血。」格拉斯憶述當時的混亂情況，「當時我也沒為意，直至我的朋友給我一塊布，我才知道我滿身是他的血」。至於獲女友從鬼門關拉回來的貝斯特，七天後可以出院，目前正療養，相信可以完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180310/large/1520670111_b5c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180310%2Flarge%2F1520670111_b5c4.jpg&h=b7e6ac7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180310/large/1520670113_6399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180310%2Flarge%2F1520670113_6399.jpg&h=6eba19e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180310/large/1520670115_6509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180310%2Flarge%2F1520670115_6509.jpg&h=6fe20028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180311/57928245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57928245&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNecn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=523933f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57928245&h=f6aa6aa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180311/57928245</a>"},{"pid":"df6b3dcfaacff7999b7a192333eb7301e9fa8edd","tid":589094,"uid":13343,"like":789,"dislike":2,"score":787,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5887b45ac97c48024f22cea1975626aa00acd0c","tid":589094,"uid":123308,"like":284,"dislike":7,"score":277,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"萬一 touch wood 救唔返會唔會變 manslaughter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf40ec395b7f3ee8d3e62524cca003970cb0685","tid":589094,"uid":146243,"like":201,"dislike":2,"score":199,"quote":{"pid":"e5887b45ac97c48024f22cea1975626aa00acd0c","tid":589094,"uid":123308,"like":284,"dislike":7,"score":277,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"萬一 touch wood 救唔返會唔會變 manslaughter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"「好撒馬利亞人法」"},{"pid":"6ca924db965f4f91765cfceb5a10834ef512618f","tid":589094,"uid":93479,"like":553,"dislike":5,"score":548,"quote":{"pid":"e5887b45ac97c48024f22cea1975626aa00acd0c","tid":589094,"uid":123308,"like":284,"dislike":7,"score":277,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"萬一 touch wood 救唔返會唔會變 manslaughter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"痴線，割喉<br />\n響極危急極緊張，簡單工具，切邊度切幾深，真係好撚難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 